<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
  <%- include('../partials/head') %>
  <style>
    .auth-container {
      max-width: 400px;
      margin: 3rem auto;
    }
    
    .auth-header {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
      color: white;
    }
    
    .auth-header h1 {
      font-size: 2rem;
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }
    
    .auth-footer {
      text-align: center;
      margin-top: 1.5rem;
      color: white;
    }
    
    .help-text {
      background: #f8f9fa;
      padding: 1rem;
      border-radius: 8px;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
      font-size: 0.875rem;
      color: #666;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <%- include('../partials/navbar') %>
  
  <main class="main-content">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="auth-container">
        <div class="auth-header">
          <h1>🔑 忘记密码</h1>
          <p>我们将发送重置链接到您的邮箱</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="card">
          <%- include('../partials/messages') %>
          
          <% if (typeof info !== 'undefined' && info && info.length > 0) { %>
            <div class="alert alert-info" style="word-break: break-all;">
              <strong>开发模式 - 重置链接：</strong><br>
              <a href="<%= info %>"><%= info %></a>
            </div>
          <% } %>
          
          <div class="help-text">
            <strong>💡 提示：</strong>请输入您注册时使用的邮箱地址。如果该邮箱存在于我们的系统中，我们将发送密码重置链接。
            <br><br>
            <strong>开发模式：</strong>重置链接将显示在控制台和页面上。
          </div>
          
          <form action="/forgot-password" method="POST">
            <div class="form-group">
              <label class="form-label" for="email">📧 邮箱地址</label>
              <input 
                type="email" 
                id="email" 
                name="email" 
                class="form-control" 
                placeholder="请输入注册邮箱"
                required
              >
            </div>
            
            <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary btn-block">发送重置链接</button>
          </form>
          
          <div style="text-align: center; margin-top: 1.5rem;">
            <a href="/login" class="text-link">← 返回登录</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</body>
</html>
